: Nazmul Arifin Rasel\nPublished Date: 2026-02-01T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://fahimtechsolutions.com/how-to-fix-windows-11-high-memory-usage-for-gaming-the-complete-optimization-guide-2026/\nText: How to Fix Windows 11 High Memory Usage for Gaming: The Complete Optimization Guide (2026) - Fahim Tech Solutions\n\nYou’re mid-match. Everything is running beautifully. Then — out of nowhere — your game stutters, freezes for two agonizing seconds, and you lose. Again.\n\nYou open Task Manager. And there it is: your memory usage sitting at 91%. Not because of your game. Because of Windows.\n\nI’ve been there. Last year, I upgraded my RAM expecting a massive performance boost — and felt almost nothing. It wasn’t until I actually dug into what Windows 11 was doing in the background that I found the real problem. Processes I’d never heard of were quietly eating gigabytes of RAM before my game even fully loaded.\n\nHere’s the thing most guides won’t tell you: the issue usually isn’t your hardware. It’s how Windows 11 manages memory in the background. And once you know exactly where to look and what to change, you can free up 1–3 GB of RAM without s\n\nTitle: ✅Fix High RAM Usage on Windows | Optimize Memory in 2026\nAuthor: ilmu sosial\nPublished Date: 2026-02-12T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://operavps.com/blog/manage-overuse-ram/\nText: ✅Fix High RAM Usage on Windows | Optimize Memory in 2026 --\n\n- Live Chat\n- Contact Us --\n\n--\n\n# Fix High RAM Usage on Windows | Optimize Memory\n\nIf your PC is slow, freezing, or showing errors like`There is not enough memory to complete this operation` your system may be experiencing excessive RAM usage.\n\nThis updated 2026 guide explains:\n\n- When to upgrade physical memory\n- How to optimize RAM usage\n- How to manage and free up memory\n- Why Windows is using too much RAM\n- Locations\n\nTable of Contents\n\nToggle\n\n## What Is RAM | Random Access Memory?\n\nRAM is one of the most important components in the system, called temporary memory, and stores data temporarily. For example, if you copy a text and restart the system, if you want to paste the text, your system will not be able to do that because RAM is a temporary memory.\n\nAlso if you have to run the software smoothly and quickly, for example, Photoshop software, the RAM in the system can help you. In this case, RAM (random access memory) can help you run programs faster without any lag.\n\n### What Is Nor\n\nTitle: 12 effective ways to fix high RAM usage on Windows 11 - Pureinfotech\nAuthor: Mauro Huculak\nPublished Date: 2026-03-02T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://pureinfotech.com/fix-high-memory-usage-windows-11/\nText: 12 effective ways to fix high RAM usage on Windows 11 - Pureinfotech\n\n- Tiny11 can lower system requirements, but is intended primarily for testing scenarios.\n- If optimization fails, resetting or reinstalling Windows 11 restores a clean performance baseline.\n- Updating Windows 11, drivers, and apps can fix memory leaks and improve stability.\n- Uninstalling unused apps and disabling unnecessary services lowers persistent RAM consumption.\n- You can reduce memory usage by disabling startup programs and limiting background app permissions.\n- When physical memory runs low, the operating system uses virtual memory, which significantly slows performance.\n- High RAM usage on Windows 11 is often caused by startup apps, background processes, outdated drivers, malware, or memory leaks.\n\nOn Windows 11, it’s possible to lower the RAM usage to improve the system and app performance, and in this guide, I’ll outline the different ways to complete the task.\n\nAlthough on modern hardware, high memory usage can slowly reduce performance. As a\n\nTitle: Windows 11 Slow Performance Fix: 15 Proven Methods (2026 Guide) - Techarticle\nAuthor: admin@techarticle.net\nPublished Date: 2026-03-02T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://techarticle.net/windows-11-slow-performance-fix-15-proven-methods-2026-guide/\nText: Windows 11 Slow Performance Fix: 15 Proven Methods (2026 Guide) - Techarticle\n\nTechArticle\n\nMore\n\n- SPORTS\n- COMPUTER\n- LIFESTYLE\n- GAMES\n- HOME IMPROVEMENT\n\nNo Result\n\nView All Result\n\nTechArticle\n\n# Windows 11 Slow Performance Fix: 15 Proven Methods (2026 Guide)\n\nby [[email protected]]\n\nMarch 2, 2026\n\nin INTERNET\n\n0\n\n305\n\nSHARES\n\n2.3k\n\nVIEWS\n\nShare on Facebook Share on Twitter\n\nIs your PC lagging? Revive it with these 15 expert-tested tweaks from quick settings to deep optimizations.\n\n15\n\nProven Fixes\n\n5min\n\nQuick Wins\n\n24H2\n\nLatest Update\n\nJump to the Fixes →\n\nTable of Contents\n\nToggle\n\n## Why Windows 11 Slows Down (And How to Fix It)\n\n### The Problem\n\nEven the best-optimized PCs can slow down over time. Bloatware, startup clutter, outdated drivers, and hidden system settings can cripple performance. Windows 11’s advanced features, like VBS and virtual machine platform, can also consume resources unnecessarily . This guide cuts through the noise with 15 proven methods to restor\n\nTitle: 14 Proven Fixes to Make Windows 11 Lightning Fast | PCMag\nPublished Date: 2026-03-02T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: http://securitywatch.pcmag.com/explainers/11-proven-fixes-to-make-windows-11-lightning-fast\nText: 14 Proven Fixes to Make Windows 11 Lightning Fast | PCMag\n\nWindows\",\"title\":\"14 Proven Fixes to Make Windows 11 Lightning Fast\",\"first_published_at\":\"2015-11-03\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-02\",\"word_count\":2076,\"days_since_updated\":16,\"weeks_since_updated\":2,\"days_since_originally_published\":3788,\"weeks_since_originally_published\":541,\"focus_keyword\":\"How to speed up Windows\",\"series\":\"Windows 11\"}},{\"title\":\"Installing Software From an ISO File? Follow This Simple, Step-by-Step Guide\",\"slug\":\"/how-to/install-a-software-program-from-an-iso-file\",\"canonical_url\":\"https://www.pcmag.com/how-to/install-a-software-program-from-an-iso-file\",\"analytics\":{\"template\":\"article-page\",\"object_type\":\"article\",\"